Text.string: You know what I like? Money. No, it's true!
They say the love of money is the root of all money.
Everyone has a price. You look like yours is loose change.
You see something you like, better have the money to pay for it! Looking is free, but it shouldn't be.
The best things in life are free, because then you can sell them for a huge markup!
People say I'm a greedy, penny-pinching miser and you know what? I love that.
As a 7th generation merchant, I've always thought about having a little 8th generation merchant to manage the family business. I've even picked out a name: Varcus. Works for boys AND girls!
Come on, what are you standin' around for? Buy something already!
So you want to hear a story, eh? Well, too bad! This is Marcus time!
You know what I miss about the old country? The suckers. Sure, there are suckers here, but the quality!
Good eye.
I have one of those myself.
Excellent choice!
Like what you see?
Only the best for you, eh?
You know a bargain when you see one.
Last one left in stock, I promise.
Better move fast!
You have chosen... wisely.
Treat yourself!
Gee, thanks, I guess.
Someone's been busy!
Nice haul. Now buy something!
You sure you don't want store credit?
Marcus Munitions: turn those guns into funds!
Ha! You're a terrible negotiator.
Any item, anywhere: sell to me, and I'll find a buyer!
Inventory comes and goes, but you can't beat cash!
Don't spend that all in one place! Except right here.
Lining your pockets won't make them bulletproof, you know.
I've got bullets with your name on them! Well, wait, that came out wrong.
You've got enemies, and I've got ammo.
Bullets and bombs!
Ask about our one-click buying plan! When your trigger goes click, it's time to buy!
Ammo! Without it, you're just a schmuck with a paperweight.
You'll be back!
Happy to help!
You know where to find me!
Always a pleasure, Vault Hunter!
Shoot more: shop Marcus!
May they bring you many kills!
A fair price for peace of mind!
Now get outta here. That ammo won't shoot itself!
Nobody does bullets better than Marcus Munitions!
No refunds!
Suit yourself!
What, you don't like money?
Everybody makes mistakes! Just don't do it again.
There's no “take-backsies” in business!
If you're looking for a better price, have I got news for you!
Did you want a bag for that?
Your money is always welcome!
Just don't drop that too close to my machines.
A fine choice!
Now, go blow something up!
Opportunity strikes again!
At this price, you can't afford to NOT buy it!
Trust your friend Marcus. You want what I'm selling.
No window shopping. Buy something or beat it!
Another day, another once-in-a-lifetime deal from Marcus Munitions!
This sale made possible in part by Vault Hunters like you.
This beauty can be yours for a steal!
I tell you, no telling WHAT is gonna come through that door.
Your friend was looking to sell, if you're looking to buy.
Why trade directly when you have a perfectly good middleman?
Cha-ching! That's the sound of opportunity!
Whatever it is, I'll take it!
Save room for the good stuff. Sell your junk at Marcus Munitions!
Enjoy your profit, my friend!
Spend it in good health.
Okay, you twisted my arm.
Impulse buys are the best buys!
There, you feel better now?
That's a good deal!
Cha-ching! Uh, I mean... nice thing!
It suits you.
Let's do this again all the time soon.
Ours is my favorite kind of relationship.
You I like.
And balance is restored once again.
Everyone has their price.
No questions asked.
Have some money. Now, why not spend it?
I used to have one just like that.
Support local business—sell to Marcus!
Vault Hunter!
My favorite customer!
Welcome!
Come in, come in! Buy something.
Ah, there you are!
Vault Hunters need to carry a lot of stuff. Carry more with an SDU!
You've got two choices: buy an SDU, or don't. But you definitely should!
Buy this thing and hold more stuff! You know you want to!
All I'm saying is, if you don't buy an SDU, you're probably going to die.
This is one of the best SDUs money can buy. So get to buying it!
Need to hold more stuff? I've got three words for you: Storage Deck Upgrade.
Being a mercenary is like being a merchant: you won't last long if you can't stay well-stocked!
SDU stands for “Super Duper Useful”. Trust me, you want it.
Staring at it won't change the price, friend!
You're gonna need more space, so buy it already!
Ah, a fine start, but will it be enough? Eh, probably not...
Excellent choice, friend!
Enjoy! No refunds. Seriously.
Now that you can carry more, you can buy more to carry! Funny how that works, eh?
With that upgrade, you can hold more items. Ammo? Whatever. You gonna buy something else or not?
For your convenience, I installed your new SDU when you weren't looking. No need to thank me.
One step closer to your true potential!
Ooh, that's a good one! Collect them all!
Better buy up the rest quick! This is very limited stock.
Very nice! Now, load up—perhaps at one of my vending machines?
Sorry, friend. You know I'd sell you more if I could.
You're fully upgraded! Why not purchase any of these other fine products?
Eh, that one's out of stock, but if you want, you can always buy something else!
If you want to carry more stuff, you'll have to buy a different SDU!
We ain't got no more!
Try something else, dummy.
You already bought all of those!
That's all I've got!
You've got as much as anyone could handle.
You can't upgrade that anymore! Sheesh!
I need an SDU for my SDUs. You've bought everything I have!
Ha! Can't believe I finally unloaded that stock. I stopped ordering new SDUs ages ago!
What, you want to carry even more stuff? Well, too bad, you can't! I'm out! So scram!
You want more SDUs? Come on now, Vault Hunter, don't be greedy.
I'm out of stock. If that's not enough bullets, bank, or backpack space to save the universe, we're in trouble.
So long, customer.
Now walk away.
Back to practicing my solitude.
Do that thing I like where you leave.
Make like one of my checks and bounce.
Off you go, then.
Fine, be that way.
The Vaults are calling, eh?
This was fun. Wait, no. What's the word? Tolerable.
Don't be a stranger. Unless you're broke. Then strange away!
Firearms in every flavor, at Marcus Munitions!
Guns for every occasion!
You could always use another gun!
Another beautiful day in the military industrial complex!
Guns! What more could you want?
They might look small, but they're actually just far away!
Now go kill the other guys!
Tell your friends! And your enemies!
Check back later for more fantastic deals!
I'm sure we'll be doing this all again soon enough.
Your business is always appreciated!
Just this once.
Come back when you mean business.
You want to KEEP that thing?
Take your time, my prices don't change!
You'll never make money if you can't make a sale.
Ah, that new gun smell!
Another victory for capitalism!
One more satisfied customer!
No questions asked, or I'll have you killed!
You won't be disappointed!
Lots of interested buyers on that, just so you know.
I see you recognize a great deal when you see one.
Buy it before it's gone!
If you don't buy it, your enemies will.
Yours, for the low low price of—well, you can read.
Your friends have good taste! See for yourself...
Refurbished, reloaded, and repriced for your convenience!
Fresh from another Vault Hunter! Alive, this time!
Your friend wanted you to have this. But they also wanted my money.
Don't worry, I didn't loot THIS one off a corpse.
